title: Europe’s Leaders Gather At Munich Summit, Reeling From Trump’s Criticism
summary_full: Officials gather on Friday for Europe’s biggest annual security summit, where a speech by Vice President JD Vance last year started an unraveling of trans-Atlantic relations.
